data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this immaculate, recently constructed one-level home.   Built by David Hodes, this house boasts contemporary design, featuring an open floor plan with spacious rooms flooded in natural light.  The sleek kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with two islands.  With attention to detail evident throughout, this home offers great style and comfort.  This home is a rare gem waiting to be yours.
